fields.form_description:
In addition to celebrating IEEE Day 2023, the IEEE NSU Student Branch- INSB brings its “IEEE Day 2023 Membership Renewal Campaign” program, starting on 15th October 2023. This program will open the way to an exclusive platform where INSB members can renew their membership for 2024, explore exciting benefits, and engage with fellow IEEE enthusiasts. 

Renew your IEEE Membership and other societies and affinity groups subscriptions with us to continue developing your career, accessing essential networking opportunities, and receiving other exclusive IEEE benefits for the calendar year of 2024!

fields.third_layer_text: Our community welcomes you to boast your innovativeness through tech competitions and informative conferences. Moreover, expanding your leadership, communication and networking competencies.

fields.award_description: We are delighted and exhilarated to announce that the IEEE NSU Student Branch has been named the winner of the IEEE Day 2022 Photo Contest. Upon the celebrations of IEEE Day 2022 and on the contests of IEEE Day, the IEEE NSU Student Branch has submitted a total of three photos under the ‘Technical Activity Category’ and the ‘Social Event Category’ each. With the participation and submission of photos, the IEEE NSU Student Branch announced Winner under the photo submission of the ‘Technical Activity Category’. A photo taken at the ‘Project Showcase’ organized by IEEE RAS SBC for the IEEE Day 2022 was submitted and awarded the First prize. Together with wishing the Student Branch success in the future, we appreciate and congratulate each member of the IEEE NSU Student Branch.

fields.award_name: IEEE R10 Exemplary Student Branch Award
fields.award_description: The IEEE R10 Exemplary Student Branch Award is given to a student branch that has maintained membership, provided student members with opportunities to volunteer, and promoted IEEE and its mission. This award aims to identify the Student Branch that has conducted quality events, workshops, projects, etc., for students' benefit. You'll be glad to know that the IEEE NSU Student Branch was able to win this award in 2019 from IEEE Region 10.
